{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_MAR_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x27,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, are you here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello Marion. Are you here about another investigation?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha... Does it look like I only care about work?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "S-Sorry. I've just never seen you when you're not working."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. That's a serious problem...<CR>I look like a woman who only lives<CR>for her work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No, I don't think you \"only\" live for your work...I think."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Plus, working ladies are very cool!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...Let me tell you an old story.<CR>I used to have a superior I looked<CR>up to in the same department."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "She found her purpose in life with her job, showed no interest in relationships, and continued to work."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "And thanks to that, she's the top achiever in her department."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That's a nice story. Like, as long as you work hard, you can achieve your goals..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "No, it's not done. She told me,<CR>\"I should've gotten married.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I-I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "And she told me again and again not to follow down the same path that she did."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xe9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That probably means I shouldn't just be doing my work so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I don't know. I'm not sure if I understand it all that well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xec,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I'm still fine. I still have a chance... I'll be okay."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xed,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "...Oh, right. I came here to see how you were doing today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "So, how's it been? Was the book I gave you useful?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yes, very! I feel like I understand a little more about alchemy now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I see. That's amazing. To be able to read such a difficult book..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I couldn't comprehend a single thing in that book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "It was written in an ancient language, so it'd be hard for anyone to read it on their first try."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "My grandfather taught me how to read that ancient language."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I see. I wonder if your grandfather was a skilled alchemist..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I don't know. He told me he was an apothecary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, Marion, the book you gave me was really helpful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I don't know too much about alchemy,<CR>but this person told me to study more about it... Ah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "About the person you're looking for, I...I've met him..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x99,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Really!? Wh-Where?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "At the ruin behind my workshop.<CR>He seemed to be investigating it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x9b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Huh, at that ruin? I should've gone there sooner..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Umm, that person...what did he do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Illegal excavation of a government ruin, property damage, breaking into government facilities, and much more."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, if you see that man again,<CR>you shouldn't get too close."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure he wouldn't harm ordinary people, but that still doesn't change the fact that he's dangerous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, but he doesn't seem that bad of a person...I think...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "(And Marion is thinking about her work again...)"
        }
    ]
}